@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
[*] --> Draft
Draft --> Processing : submit
Processing --> Completed : confirm
Completed --> Cancelled : approve
Completed : entry / log report
Cancelled --> OnHold : update
Cancelled : entry / log report
OnHold --> Rejected : process
OnHold --> Cancelled : revert
Rejected --> [*]
@enduml